  "body": "Pin Python to 3.13.11 in the CodSpeed benchmark job. CPython 3.13.12 introduced a segfault in CodSpeed's walltime callgraph post-processing ([CodSpeedHQ/pytest-codspeed#106](https://github.com/CodSpeedHQ/pytest-codspeed/issues/106)), causing all `libs/core` benchmark runs to fail with `exit status: 139` since Feb 26 despite all 13 benchmarks passing.",
